snippet.title: Hyper Princess Pitch trailer - Remar Games
snippet.description:
Download: http://www.remar.se/daniel/pitch.php

The official trailer for Hyper Princess Pitch by Remar Games. Music by Niklas Ström (finurligaljud.se)

This game is freeware and a tribute to DOS Operation: Carnage, one of my favourite games. Supported by Windows 98, XP, Vista, 7 and 10.
